The paper deals with combinatorial auctions, which are a topic in game theory (cs.GT) and involve optimization problems (cs.DS). The mechanism design aspect of the paper suggests that it could also belong to the artificial intelligence (cs.AI) category. The use of communication protocols in the mechanism design suggests that it could also belong to the information theory (cs.IT) category.
